# Dashboard UI Standards

## Design System
- **Component Library**: shadcn/ui components
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Language**: Turkish UI labels
- **Theme**: Dark/Light mode support via [ThemeContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/ThemeContext.tsx)

## Layout Patterns

### Main Dashboard Structure
```typescript
// Dashboard.tsx - Main layout
<div className="min-h-screen bg-background">
  <Navbar />
  <div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-6">
    {/* Tab content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

### KPI Cards Grid
```typescript
// Responsive grid layout
<div className="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
  {kpiCards.map(card => <EditableKPICard />)}
</div>
```

### Accordion Tables
```typescript
// Expandable table sections
<div className="space-y-4">
  {gameGroups.map(group => (
    <AccordionItem key={group.id}>
      <AccordionTrigger>{group.title}</AccordionTrigger>
      <AccordionContent>
        <GameTables data={group.dailyData} />
      </AccordionContent>
    </AccordionItem>
  ))}
</div>
```

## Component Standards

### Button Variants
- `default`: Primary actions
- `outline`: Secondary actions  
- `ghost`: Subtle actions
- `destructive`: Delete/danger actions

### Card Components
- Use `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter`
- Consistent padding and spacing
- Proper semantic structure

### Form Elements
- Use `Input`, `Label`, `Select` from shadcn/ui
- Consistent validation states
- Turkish placeholder text

## Responsive Design
- **Mobile**: Single column layout, stacked components
- **Tablet**: 2-column grid for KPI cards
- **Desktop**: 4-column grid for KPI cards, side-by-side tables

## Color Scheme
- **Primary**: Blue tones for interactive elements
- **Success**: Green for positive metrics
- **Warning**: Orange for caution states
- **Error**: Red for negative metrics
- **Muted**: Gray for secondary information

## Typography
- **Headings**: Font-semibold for section titles
- **Body**: Default font weight for content
- **Captions**: Text-sm for metadata
- **Numbers**: Monospace for KPI values

## Accessibility
- Proper ARIA labels for interactive elements
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader friendly
- High contrast ratios

## Critical Rules
- ✅ Always use shadcn/ui components
- ✅ Follow Tailwind CSS patterns
- ✅ Use Turkish labels for user-facing text
- ✅ Maintain consistent spacing (gap-4, py-6, etc.)
- ✅ Test responsive behavior on all screen sizes
- ✅ Ensure proper semantic HTML structure
- ✅ Use proper color contrast ratios

